{"tid":778158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18年冤獄疑雲或現轉機 林鄭今去信菲總統促正視鄧龍威案","createTime":"2018-08-13T12:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T01:32:03.000Z","uid":74058,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"777733f19711a7b1fd452450c9a28c4d2602d302","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180813/58559140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58559140&d=7GYNeQdfKZmjoufRQVFgpjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=80a86122\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58559140&h=955930d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180813/58559140</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180813/large/1534161438_f8a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180813%2Flarge%2F1534161438_f8a0.png&h=5ad97505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港人鄧龍威2000年被指在菲律賓藏毒，遭扣留長達11年直到2011才受審，被判罪成及終身監禁，但他一直堅稱自己含冤入獄，早前其胞兄鄧龍彪以及「鄧龍威事件關注組」成員曾到政府總部請願，並去信特首林鄭月娥，希望林鄭可以促請保安局為其胞弟提供當年出入境紀錄證明。立法會議員謝偉俊今日公佈案件最新消息，表示因應該案終審上訴限期迫近，特首已於今日去信菲律賓總統，要求總統正視鄧龍威一案，以及責成菲律賓移民局提供他於2000年入境菲律賓記錄。<br />\n謝偉俊指，今日收到特首信件副本，而根據他早前寄給菲律賓移民局信件，保安局局長李家超於8月10日再致函菲移民局、駐菲律賓中國領事館及菲律賓駐港領使館，要求關鍵出入境記錄。謝形容消息令人鼓舞，相信菲律賓總統會適時回應。<br />\n今年8月3日，菲律賓最高法院要求鄧龍威在10日內提交上訴書以及交出新證據，否則最高法院極有可能維持原判。胞兄鄧龍彪曾表示，過去曾多次要求入境處及保安局提供該出入境紀錄，但保安局回覆指所有10年前的出入境紀錄已銷毀，令他們感到極度失望。去年當地法庭文件披露內容，揭示菲律賓警方曾在法庭上聲稱2000年6月1日起曾於馬尼拉監視鄧龍威12天，但事實上當時鄧人在香港，故不可能「被監視」，顯示菲警有虛構證供嫌疑，「鄧龍威事件關注組」及謝偉俊曾就此促請港府，盡快提供當年鄧的出境紀錄，以取得「不在場證明」進行終極上訴。 <img src=\"https://staticlayout.appledaily.hk/web_images/layout/art_end.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstaticlayout.appledaily.hk%2Fweb_images%2Flayout%2Fart_end.gif&h=d6886982&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a635792abfd311bf17fae1cb1483304270723d8","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701fede4ef1d53eba855edfb69d4b3e740940e91","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09269d812a60ad03a095a7cf03ff6abf8e8bb54f","tid":778158,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"好慘"},{"pid":"d468650a5ede7408adf6b62fb38d57e7f8f0db53","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"如果係689，一定眼尾都唔望下"},{"pid":"8dbb9e5476604fecf41dc84ff53b011b45a50e50","tid":778158,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"d7a7534b306a02690bb11ec2c00cc227e87f90ba","tid":778158,"uid":28155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d468650a5ede7408adf6b62fb38d57e7f8f0db53","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"如果係689，一定眼尾都唔望下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"冇望5年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ef49e321da163726fba1c70e513c063ffaf236","tid":778158,"uid":113626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總算為本土香港人做返d野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9d1df990ed3592897106fbe2a6277185babcb6","tid":778158,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a7534b306a02690bb11ec2c00cc227e87f90ba","tid":778158,"uid":28155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d468650a5ede7408adf6b62fb38d57e7f8f0db53","t